<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA85">
<l>kaṇṇārak kaṇṭumeṉ kaiyārak kūppiyu</l>
<l>meṇṇāra veṇṇattā leṇṇiyum - viṇṇō</l>
<l>ṉeriyāṭi yeṉṟeṉṟu miṉpuṟuvaṉ kollō</l>
<l>periyāṉaik kāṇap peṟiṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Shall I see [him to my] eyes’ fill, shall I fold my hands to [their] fill,</l>
<l>shall I think [him] with thoughts to [my] mind’s fill, shall I repeat</l>
<l>“celestial, fire dancer”, shall I feel pleasure</l>
<l>when I obtain to see the great one?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
